"<1.so>Argh! <2.pa>Please...<3.pa>get off that horse!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>*ahem* <5.pa>I'm sorry.<6.pa> I'm just worried you'll\n"
"scare the sheep."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
